{"tid":739067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SpaceX Elon Musk：別再叫我“億萬富翁”了 這個詞是貶義","createTime":"2018-07-12T00:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T00:01:45.000Z","uid":66943,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"606aeb51a4714239a93d263db18f2340128c8ec7","tid":739067,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"Tesla和SpaceX的CEO Elon Musk雖然是著名億萬富翁，但他其實不喜歡這個標籤。最近，他在Twitter上表達了媒體稱呼他為&ldquo;億萬富翁&rdquo;的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/075520_fc1330db8c6859c7a67714b758cd9a2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F075520_fc1330db8c6859c7a67714b758cd9a2c.jpg&h=0d5c138c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他在Twitter上說：<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;具有諷刺意味的是，當&ldquo;億萬富翁&rdquo;這一標籤被媒體使用時，幾乎總是意味著對報導對象的貶低和詆毀。直到我的公司達到一定的規模，他們才這樣稱呼我，但現實是我仍然和以前一樣，做著同樣的科學和工程業務，只是規模改變了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/075539_60b9ec79c38dd08180a3c855baacf824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F075539_60b9ec79c38dd08180a3c855baacf824.jpg&h=1817a09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Musk對&ldquo;億萬富翁&rdquo;這個詞的看法</span></div><br />\n<br />\n　　沒錯，雖然Musk的資產淨值為200億美元，但他認為&ldquo;億萬富翁&rdquo;這個詞在描述億萬富翁時，&ldquo;幾乎總是意味著對當事人的貶低和詆毀。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　也有Twitter說&ldquo;億萬富翁&rdquo;這個詞沒有甚麼貶義，如果Musk認為是貶義的，可能是Musk覺得這個詞意味著從世界其它地方攫取大量金錢和資源。對此，Musk反駁道：<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;不，這意味著我直接為5萬人創造了就業機會，並通過零件供應商和相關行業，間接地為2.5萬人提供工作崗位，從而支持了上百萬個家庭。你做了甚麼？ &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/075612_31ecccd4a6768c04f0f743d2c5f3b342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F075612_31ecccd4a6768c04f0f743d2c5f3b342.jpg&h=ed6d3275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　此前，Musk曾關注泰國足球隊員被困溶洞時間，並聲稱一直在與潛水員團隊溝通，SpaceX和The Boring Company的工程師團隊已經前往泰國參與救援，同時帶去了緊急趕製的迷你潛水艇，但救援任務負責人認為，這艘潛艇值得讚賞但並不實用。Musk堅持將潛艇留在山洞裡，&ldquo;以防將來有用。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"2ece68dc7f22a58031e793e2aa236031b68244bc","tid":739067,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"捐咗佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623de025bdf64c359b93b5ae196457cd21b5a413","tid":739067,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946b7c3fd6c447612923b08d8aa047a7ec729e3b","tid":739067,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a58a4098e21abdb18f31126e93f77cf5ed5a374","tid":739067,"uid":77355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ece68dc7f22a58031e793e2aa236031b68244bc","tid":739067,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"捐咗佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"好膚淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc1612fa5895a03d813da8c42342f7f12c9291d","tid":739067,"uid":51388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"事實嚟"},{"pid":"c95046f6a09671f9ce8bc220577c613d4cdff0fe","tid":739067,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8a58a4098e21abdb18f31126e93f77cf5ed5a374","tid":739067,"uid":77355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ece68dc7f22a58031e793e2aa236031b68244bc","tid":739067,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"捐咗佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"reply